Replace 12.4 and 4.7 with 11 and 6.8 respectively (the values you used in your voltage divider). Your resistor combination for VD also steps down voltage to 4.5v instead of 5v. Hence, calculated battery percentage won&#39;t be accurate. Use resistor combination for VD that steps down voltage close to 5v.

